relevant_findings.general: A&O (Alert and Oriented), NAD (No Acute Distress)
relevant_findings.HEENT: No scleral icterus, mucus membranes moist
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: RRR (Regular Rate and Rhythm), no murmurs, rubs, or gallops appreciated
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, normal work of breathing
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, non-distended, tenderness to palpation in RLQ (Right Lower Quadrant), no rebound or guarding, negative psoas and obturator signs, no organomegaly appreciated
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused
